'''RNA聚合酶Ⅱ'''（{{lang-en|RNA polymerase II}}，亦被称为'''RNAPⅡ'''或'''PolⅡ'''）是一个[[蛋白质复合体|多种蛋白质复合体]]。它是在[[真核生物|真核生物]]细胞核中发现的三种[[RNA聚合酶|RNAP]][[酶|酶]]之一<ref name=":0" />。 它催化[[脱氧核糖核酸|DNA]]的转录，以合成[[mRNA|mRNA]]的和大多数[[snRNA|snRNA]]和[[微RNA|微RNA]]的前体<ref name="Kornberg">{{cite journal | vauthors = Kornberg RD | title = Eukaryotic transcriptional control | journal = Trends in Cell Biology | volume = 9 | issue = 12 | pages = M46-9 | date = December 1999 | pmid = 10611681 | doi = 10.1016/S0962-8924(99)01679-7 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Sims RJ, Mandal SS, Reinberg D | title = Recent highlights of RNA-polymerase-II-mediated transcription | journal = Current Opinion in Cell Biology | volume = 16 | issue = 3 | pages = 263–71 | date = June 2004 | pmid = 15145350 | doi = 10.1016/j.ceb.2004.04.004 }}</ref>。 RNA聚合酶Ⅱ是一个550 kDa的12个亚基复合物，是研究最多的RNA聚合酶类型。 它需要多种[[转录因子|转录因子]]才能与上游基因[[启动子|启动子]]结合并开始转录。

==发现==
[[Image:RNA_polymerase_II.fcgi.png|thumb]]的RNA聚合酶Ⅱ包含有12个亚基<ref name=Meyer>{{cite journal |author=Meyer PA, Ye P, Zhang M, Suh MH, Fu J |title=Phasing RNA polymerase II using intrinsically bound Zn atoms: an updated structural model |journal=Structure. |date=Jun 2006 |volume=14 |issue=6 |pages=973–82 |url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0969212606002152 |pmid=16765890 |doi=10.1016/j.str.2006.04.003 |access-date=2014-02-05 |archive-date=2018-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180619022534/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S0969212606002152 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。]]

早期的研究表明至少有两种[[RNA聚合酶|RNAP]]：一种在核仁中合成rRNA，另一种在核质中合成其他RNA，核一部分但在核仁外<ref name=":2" />。在1969年，科学实验家罗伯特·罗德（Robert Roeder）和威廉·鲁特（William Rutter）最终发现了一种额外的[[RNA聚合酶|RNAP]]，它负责在核质中转录某种RNA。 通过使用DEAE-Sephadex {{le|离子色谱法|Ion chromatography|离子交换色谱法}}获得该发现。 该技术通过增加硫酸铵的浓度将酶分离相应洗脱的顺序，I，II，II。根据洗脱顺序命名酶，{{le|RNA聚合酶Ⅰ|RNA polymerase I}}，RNA聚合酶Ⅱ，[[RNA聚合酶III|RNA聚合酶Ⅲ]]。 该发现表明在核质中存在另外的酶，其允许RNAP II和[[RNA聚合酶III|RNAP III]]之间的区分。

== 亚基 ==
真核核心 RNA聚合酶II首先使用转录分析被纯化<ref name=Sawadogo>{{cite journal | vauthors = Sawadogo M, Sentenac A | title = RNA polymerase B (II) and general transcription factors | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_annual-review-of-biochemistry_1990_59/page/711 | journal = Annual Review of Biochemistry | volume = 59 | pages = 711–54 | year = 1990 | pmid = 2197989 | doi = 10.1146/annurev.bi.59.070190.003431 }}</ref>。 被纯化的酶通常有10-12个亚基（人类和酵母中有12个），并且不能识别特定的启动子<ref name=Myer>{{cite journal | vauthors = Myer VE, Young RA | title = RNA polymerase II holoenzymes and subcomplexes | journal = The Journal of Biological Chemistry | volume = 273 | issue = 43 | pages = 27757–60 | date = October 1998 | pmid = 9774381 | doi = 10.1074/jbc.273.43.27757 | doi-access = free }}</ref>。 许多亚基-亚基相互作用是已知的<ref name=Acker>{{cite journal | vauthors = Acker J, de Graaff M, Cheynel I, Khazak V, Kedinger C, Vigneron M | title = Interactions between the human RNA polymerase II subunits | journal = The Journal of Biological Chemistry | volume = 272 | issue = 27 | pages = 16815–21 | date = July 1997 | pmid = 9201987 | doi = 10.1074/jbc.272.27.16815 | doi-access = free }}</ref>。

